Running SURVIVOR SVsim Requires...
1: Reference fasta file
2: Parameter file
3: SNP mutations frequency (0-1)
4: 0= simulated reads; 1= real reads
	** NOTE: It depends if you want to alter the reference and simulate
	reads based on this to map it back to the original reference to 
	evaluate the SV caller (parameter 4 =0) . OR use real reads to map them
	to an alternated genome to evaluate the SV caller. (parameter 4 =1)
5: output prefix


$ SURVIVOR simSV ./reference_genome parameter_file 0.1 0 simulated


$ cat parameter_file 
PARAMETER FILE: DO JUST MODIFY THE VALUES AND KEEP THE SPACES!
DUPLICATION_minimum_length: 100
DUPLICATION_maximum_length: 10000
DUPLICATION_number: 10
